Adrax feels his joints loosen, he can move once more. The conversation began 
to bring him back to his senses. Pushing some rocks aside, he emerged to see 
Autofire risen.

Adrax stands to see himself in a much smaller form, a Predacon form. " I do 
not recall ending my life cycle in such a small, insignificant form as this! 
I was large, strong, a god among bots! Now, I am merely a Predacon warrior? " 

Sighing, he looks to his counterpart, "Who did this to us?"
